ec320030-4ddd-413d-8d34-2b7aa592dda7.title: <player>
ec320030-4ddd-413d-8d34-2b7aa592dda7.text:
Are you the famous Lady Keli? Leader of the toughest
gang of mercenary killers around?

b12c3b6c-8fce-4374-8128-7d238235a847.title: Lady Keli
b12c3b6c-8fce-4374-8128-7d238235a847.text: I am Keli, you have heard of me then?

options.text: Heard of you? You are famous in Gielinor!
I have heard a little, but I think Katrine is tougher.
I have heard rumours that you kill people.
No I have never really heard of you.

6ed3a3e2-6436-4385-9717-3c69f3b48720.title: <player>
6ed3a3e2-6436-4385-9717-3c69f3b48720.text:
The great Lady Keli, of course I have heard of you.
You are famous in Gielinor!

c5c458a0-3d09-4f6a-abfe-1bc248f35c46.title: Lady Keli
c5c458a0-3d09-4f6a-abfe-1bc248f35c46.text:
That's very kind of you to say. Reputations are
not easily earned. I have managed to succeed
where many fail.

options.text: I think Katrine is still tougher.
What is your latest plan then?
You must have trained a lot for this work.
I should not disturb someone as tough as you.

02849405-c087-4c32-a3c8-06cc88c3a5b2.title: <player>
02849405-c087-4c32-a3c8-06cc88c3a5b2.text: I think Katrine is still tougher.

99c76190-949f-4e85-b71d-aa01495f2907.title: Lady Keli
99c76190-949f-4e85-b71d-aa01495f2907.text:
Well you can think that all you like. I know those
blackarm cowards dare not leave the city. Out here, I
am toughest. You can tell them that! Now get out of
my sight, before I call my guards.

1be85183-dc50-4106-bdc4-3f23a07e43b8.title: <player>
1be85183-dc50-4106-bdc4-3f23a07e43b8.text: I have heard rumours that you kill people.

d48be9e1-0d91-4f3c-979e-2e165307f590.title: Lady Keli
d48be9e1-0d91-4f3c-979e-2e165307f590.text:
There's always someone ready to spread rumours. I
hear all sort of ridiculous things these days.

459d7bd0-aca2-40d0-9604-f65f84ec583b.title: <player>
459d7bd0-aca2-40d0-9604-f65f84ec583b.text:
What is your latest plan then? Of course, you need
not go into specific details.

7fcae09a-bdde-400e-95dd-107f66ffaeaa.title: Lady Keli
7fcae09a-bdde-400e-95dd-107f66ffaeaa.text:
Well, I can tell you I have a valuable prisoner here
in my cells.

7a080b01-af88-457d-a885-c6c046b03d39.title: Lady Keli
7a080b01-af88-457d-a885-c6c046b03d39.text:
I can expect a high reward to be paid very soon for
this guy. I can't tell you who he is, but he is a lot
colder now.

options.text: Ah, I see. You must have been very skillful.
That's great, are you sure they will pay?
Can you be sure they will not try to get him out?
I should not disturb someone as tough as you.

20c4747c-be39-44cd-8fb6-62738cda55b3.title: <player>
20c4747c-be39-44cd-8fb6-62738cda55b3.text: You must have been very skillful.

533a6b76-37ce-479a-8769-a61babd7d88f.title: Lady Keli
533a6b76-37ce-479a-8769-a61babd7d88f.text: Yes, I did most of the work. We had to grab the Pr...

562b0255-72e3-48b7-9b30-36cf16a46dc4.title: Lady Keli
562b0255-72e3-48b7-9b30-36cf16a46dc4.text:
Er, we had to grab him without his ten bodyguards
noticing. It was a stroke of genius.

options.text: Are you sure they will pay?
Can you be sure they will not try to get him out?
I should not disturb someone as tough as you.

d1cbd205-eb3b-4aff-918c-c0e788eae4e8.title: <player>
d1cbd205-eb3b-4aff-918c-c0e788eae4e8.text: Are you sure they will pay?

0d311e5c-bf23-47a2-b7cb-12ada2843719.title: Lady Keli
0d311e5c-bf23-47a2-b7cb-12ada2843719.text:
They will pay, or we will cut his hair off and send it to
them.

27533f14-a836-49da-9e92-c11ef96142f8.title: <player>
27533f14-a836-49da-9e92-c11ef96142f8.text:
How about trying something tougher? Maybe cut his
finger off?

ac0f87a5-8648-4d39-8569-51ff7633588e.title: Lady Keli
ac0f87a5-8648-4d39-8569-51ff7633588e.text:
That's a good idea, I could use talented people like you.
I may call on you if I need work doing.

options.text: You must have been very skillful.
Can you be sure they will not try to get him out?
I should not disturb someone as tough as you.

f7b3b8bc-4ae8-45f5-8c51-0d19222b99c4.title: <player>
f7b3b8bc-4ae8-45f5-8c51-0d19222b99c4.text: Can you be sure they will not try to get him out?

fb3b3956-1760-4fbc-9f5a-bf3408096e86.title: Lady Keli
fb3b3956-1760-4fbc-9f5a-bf3408096e86.text:
There is no way to release him. The only key to the
door is on a chain around my neck and the locksmith
who made the lock died suddenly when he had finished.

e0c0444e-7f25-4d05-affe-d3b84a72b151.title: Lady Keli
e0c0444e-7f25-4d05-affe-d3b84a72b151.text: There is not another key like this in the world.

options.text: Could I see the key please?
That is a good way to keep secrets.
I should not disturb someone as tough as you.

d6d01ccf-25a6-46a8-b2e3-21898329615a.title: <player>
d6d01ccf-25a6-46a8-b2e3-21898329615a.text:
Could I see the key please? Just for a moment. It
would be something I can tell my grandchildren. When
you are even more famous than you are now.

84c5b5dd-eede-47aa-893b-b434fd554d1f.title: Lady Keli
84c5b5dd-eede-47aa-893b-b434fd554d1f.text:
As you put it that way I am sure you can see it. You
cannot steal the key, it is on a Runite chain.

options.text: Could I touch the key for a moment please?
I should not disturb someone as tough as you.

90487dfa-594e-486a-9276-758c73d847a1.title: <player>
90487dfa-594e-486a-9276-758c73d847a1.text: Could I touch the key a moment please?

76ed48e4-5b0b-4921-827e-5b98fc0236ac.text:
Keli passes you the key, you press it into the
soft clay before handing it back.

11f4fbc2-1f2e-49a0-8828-8f8735dccbb2.title: <player>
11f4fbc2-1f2e-49a0-8828-8f8735dccbb2.text: Thank you so much, you are too kind, o great Keli.

033bf913-6f65-4497-9279-ea0e9311ba43.title: Lady Keli
033bf913-6f65-4497-9279-ea0e9311ba43.text: You are welcome, run along now, I am very busy.

f771bbcc-6bd0-4e74-86c8-250150ef24c9.text:
Keli passes you the key, you inspect it for
a few seconds before handing it back.

4f197b78-199d-4d04-83ec-124a214d8ffe.title: <player>
4f197b78-199d-4d04-83ec-124a214d8ffe.text: That is a good way to keep secrets.

edd85c16-380c-4812-b283-0f5e43746969.title: Lady Keli
edd85c16-380c-4812-b283-0f5e43746969.text: It is the best way I know. Dead men tell no tales.

e20b00ef-6fce-4479-9485-534070436eb2.title: <player>
e20b00ef-6fce-4479-9485-534070436eb2.text: I am glad I know none of your secrets, Keli.

bf33d06d-477e-4289-9d76-58708f4f41d5.title: <player>
bf33d06d-477e-4289-9d76-58708f4f41d5.text: I should not disturb someone as tough as you.

a46e7198-381c-4a2e-abb9-c579149ca615.title: Lady Keli
a46e7198-381c-4a2e-abb9-c579149ca615.text:
I need to do a lot of work, goodbye. When you get a
little tougher, maybe I will give you a job.

439648a2-9ae7-4e0a-981d-82e609cc3ff3.title: <player>
439648a2-9ae7-4e0a-981d-82e609cc3ff3.text: You must have trained a lot for this work.

ff0f6e81-789c-4d6e-9bdb-93047eb4e8c9.title: Lady Keli
ff0f6e81-789c-4d6e-9bdb-93047eb4e8c9.text:
I have used a sword since I was a small girl. I stabbed
three people before I was 6 years old.

options.text: What is your latest plan then?
You must have trained a lot for this work.
I think Katrine is still tougher.
I should not disturb someone as tough as you.

0985d954-7e0e-472e-8697-a0b628463556.title: <player>
0985d954-7e0e-472e-8697-a0b628463556.text: No I have never really heard of you.

88b77ec7-2930-4795-9199-cdfa067fc2ba.title: Lady Keli
88b77ec7-2930-4795-9199-cdfa067fc2ba.text:
You must be new to this land then. EVERYONE
knows of Lady Keli and her prowess with the sword.

options.text: No, still doesn't ring a bell.
Yes, of course I have heard of you.
You must have trained a lot for this work.
I should not disturb someone as tough as you.

901bea60-8e57-4ab6-a69c-bae47dd8b9a1.title: <player>
901bea60-8e57-4ab6-a69c-bae47dd8b9a1.text: No, your name still doesn't ring a bell.

e4dfe072-1800-4ee5-9107-212cb2aa548b.title: Lady Keli
e4dfe072-1800-4ee5-9107-212cb2aa548b.text:
Well, you know of me now. I will wring your neck if
you do not show respect.

options.text: I do not show respect to killers and hoodlums.
You must have trained a lot for this work.
I should not disturb someone as tough as you, great lady.

02c060ff-10ad-4187-9406-9da38617779e.title: <player>
02c060ff-10ad-4187-9406-9da38617779e.text: I do not show respect to killers and hoodlums.

b6659771-f253-44b5-9456-068fed8d8b4f.title: Lady Keli
b6659771-f253-44b5-9456-068fed8d8b4f.text:
You should, you really should. I am wealthy enough to
place a bounty on your head. Or just remove your
head myself. Now go, I am busy, too busy to fight a
would-be hoodlum.

args: &rYou need rope to tie her up
